{"tid":1623433,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"記唔記得batman入面的joker點對啲錢？","createTime":"2019-10-04T21:39:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-05T11:40:40.000Z","uid":4396,"like":48,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"9fe8a7ad4470398904ac3003d9b7d8687907651d","tid":1623433,"uid":4396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T21:39:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KGS7hsq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKGS7hsq.jpg&h=ba9113ce&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nJoker追求的是純粹的混沌，佢忠於佢的理念，所以視錢財如糞土。<br />\n<br />\n我地唔係joker咁的恐怖分子，我地係追求終極自由的俠義之人，我地唔會搶任何野。我寧願大家拆完店後燒左佢都唔好偷任何野！<br />\n<br />\n如果大家見到有人搶野，請打9佢同燒左佢想搶既野！<br />\n<br />\n認同請分享<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c24a1faef50977b174cc390bb893f4b8d6a8655","tid":1623433,"uid":4396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T21:40:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iJ8BVgm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiJ8BVgm.jpg&h=ab007ce0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b086a281cc113e76234ea72d9a8d6ed761df4e85","tid":1623433,"uid":4396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T21:40:36.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b9bc789dc3085337d30be3578d81469c4744b9fa","tid":1623433,"uid":4396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T21:42:56.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3c89542445812f24e1d26ccca5d126be6f175404","tid":1623433,"uid":4396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T21:44:23.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f9d0e5892c2df7403e28bfdcbb02da332f73802b","tid":1623433,"uid":4396,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T21:44:34.000Z","msg":"燒左佢"},{"pid":"d344d4f096c2db75bf1c913771f720d514c65e84","tid":1623433,"uid":226882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T22:02:00.000Z","msg":"If we burn you burn with us"},{"pid":"1035e19d19d678f5c7992dc1c